					<article id="post-14036" class="post post-14036 type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-journalism tag-animatronic-animals tag-animatronic-dinosaurs tag-jurassic-world tag-jurassic-world-3">
										<span class="entry-title" style="display: none;">The dinosaurs are coming back! Jurassic world 3 resumed shooting on July 6</span>
			
				
						<div class="post-content">
				<div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-1 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: left top;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:90px;padding-right:30px;padding-bottom:4%;padding-left:30px;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-color:#e7e4e2;border-top-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_2_3 fusion-builder-column-0 fusion-two-third fusion-column-first 2_3"  style='margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;width:66.66%;width:calc(66.66% - ( ( 4% ) * 0.6666 ) );margin-right: 4%;'><div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"   data-bg-url=""><div class="fusion-text"><h1 style="text-align: center;">According to the news on June 16, &#8220;<a href="https://g.co/kgs/njviUz">Jurassic world 3</a>: rule&#8221; will become one of the first blockbusters to be filmed in Britain.</h1>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14037" src="https://www.dinosaurjoy.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-1.jpeg" alt="" width="640" height="407" srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/artificialdinosaur/animatronic-dinosaurs/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-1-200x127.jpeg 200w, https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/artificialdinosaur/animatronic-dinosaurs/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-1-300x191.jpeg 300w, https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/artificialdinosaur/animatronic-dinosaurs/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-1-400x254.jpeg 400w, https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/artificialdinosaur/animatronic-dinosaurs/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-1-600x382.jpeg 600w, https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/artificialdinosaur/animatronic-dinosaurs/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-1.jpeg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Jurassic world 3 Poster</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">Universal Pictures confirmed that the film will resume work at the pine studio on July 6. Preparations will begin this week. It will follow the local government approved safety guidelines for resumption of work under the epidemic. People flying to the UK to film the film (including stars Chris parrat and Blaise Dallas Howard) will be isolated for two weeks.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">It is reported that &#8220;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jurassic_World:_Dominion">Jurassic world 3: rule</a>&#8220;, which started shooting in London in February this year, is scheduled to be released in North America on June 21, 2021. Directed by Colin trevoro, the first director of the series, Chris parrat and Blaise Dallas Howard continue to star.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Jurassic Park: old Kassam Neal, Laura Dunn and Jeff gobblen return.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14038" src="https://www.dinosaurjoy.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-2.jpeg" alt="" width="640" height="640" srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/artificialdinosaur/animatronic-dinosaurs/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-2-66x66.jpeg 66w, https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/artificialdinosaur/animatronic-dinosaurs/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-2-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/artificialdinosaur/animatronic-dinosaurs/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-2-200x200.jpeg 200w, https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/artificialdinosaur/animatronic-dinosaurs/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-2-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/artificialdinosaur/animatronic-dinosaurs/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-2-400x400.jpeg 400w, https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/artificialdinosaur/animatronic-dinosaurs/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-2-600x600.jpeg 600w, https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/artificialdinosaur/animatronic-dinosaurs/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Jurassic-world-3-2.jpeg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Jurassic world 3 Poster</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">In addition, Mamodo Aarthi, who has performed in the &#8220;youth hip-hop dream&#8221;, and Dewanda Wise, who has played the &#8220;has the final say&#8221;, is also a new member.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">It&#8217;s reported that when the film was launched, Chris parrat told Jurassic century that he was shocked when he first knew the proposal of Jurassic century 3, because the final result of Jurassic world: falling country made people not know how to continue the story.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">In the film, Blaise Dallas Howard&#8217;s horsetail is different from her previous horsetail in Jurassic world: falling country, with short hair and glasses.</p>
